summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2016 FORD EXPLORER. WHILE DRIVING 30 MPH, THE CONTACT OBSERVED AN ODOR UNDERNEATH THE THIRD ROW SEATS. THE CONTACT BEGAN FEELING DROWSY AND DIZZY. THE ISSUE OCCURRED SEVERAL TIMES. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO APPLE FORD LINCOLN (8800 STANFORD BLVD, COLUMBIA, MD 21045, (866) 841-9642) WHERE IT WAS DIAGNOSED AND REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 29,000.
